    "body": "Previous implementation used a full sort but this is unnecessary. Pairs do not need to be processed in id-order, all that we did was make \"start\" and \"end\" marks find each other. This can be done with a hash table instead. The \"grow only\" khash_t mentioned in the TODO is the since long merged #24985 refactor with dense value array, to not regress on memory locality.\r\n",
    "closed_at": "2026-03-04T08:04:33Z",
